4bda189948a4ae6788aec4b94094f19103","tid":1855641,"uid":136494,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"12b9ba3626f807ed169590a21196cbc37955e73d","tid":1855641,"uid":288675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30685c961d8a522e8cadf83c80cf5173efeb1fb0","tid":1855641,"uid":238330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"日常兩個人戴住口罩講野，已經安全，因為有口罩擋住飛沫。<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:15:48.000Z","msg":"口水最細 0.6 &mu;m<br />\n擋3 &mu;m 阻唔阻到 0.6&mu;m ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"你講既應該係飛沫 最細0.6 micron冇錯，bfe最多防到 3 micron都冇錯，但係因為咁樣就覺得bfe冇用係唔正確的。<br />\n<br />\nbfe的實驗方式係將細菌溝水打成霧，然後係一個規範的氣流速度內衝擊，睇口罩可以有效過濾多少細菌，所以bfe係決定口罩係咪防飛沫的基礎測試（亦都係點解bfv&gt;95%=醫學用口罩）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">換然之，既然bfe口罩係可以防止飛沫，亦等於某程度上防到病毒</span><br />\n因為病毒係要依附係水霧顆粒上先有傳染能力，冇載體的病毒係一般情況下無法造成有效感染。因此，只要呢個口罩係可以防到飛沫，咁佢係日常情況下預防武漢肺炎上就係一個好且有用的口罩（撇除高風險醫療行業，密閉空間等）<br />\n<br />\n最後回應返一般人引以為傲的PFE VFE 99%標準，就算隔慮到0.1um，但其實都仲有1%過濾唔到病毒，唔通呢d口罩又係冇用？再甚者如果有人打噴嚏你冇距離夠1米，飛沫可透過結膜傳染，咁係咪連眼睛都要帶口罩？<br />\n<br />\n最後既最後，每個人都有免疫系統，如考慮埋擴散距離，病患親密接觸性，bfe口罩係日常生活絕對夠做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab2ed5db382c253f30d042c68d0e9f4ed2acab9","tid":1855641,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7719a5710b506f071694bf25f7413a828f4cf23c","tid":1855641,"uid":59014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52b91d09b22af8d4cd48ff773f572bcc479a6d53","tid":1855641,"uid":136494,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"唔係入醫院 或者去高危疫區<br />\nBfe&gt;95%日常生活用已經好夠<br />\n比你買到3e&gt;99% 都唔代表防到99%<br />\n邊位漏氣一樣都係死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當D人再吹大D既, 係咪會話埋香港醫院係跟美國標準<br />\n其他國家乜韓國, 泰國, 印尼, 日本都唔係跟美國標準<br />\n個D乜乜柒柒測試都會有差異/廢好多<br />\n到時用緊美罩撚又出黎批逗日本罩無用 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"互片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45f12d56f1f6143d1ecb208c4ad74e059f444c1","tid":1855641,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee41b6fe875991480ebc4097207268bbc412476","tid":1855641,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"今日打邊爐單野<br />\n如果當你冇參與一齊食只係圍爐吹下水戴住罩計<br />\n咁D蒸氣會唔會都令你中招?"},{"pid":"70b7ee678c73b3a7a67fbc44eb71889d7be21259","tid":1855641,"uid":14919,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"終於有人出post講防到飛沫就夠 好感動<br />\n之前話唔洗VFE仲俾人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3338d818ed22251bca6bef74f2dd90a9e7223607","tid":1855641,"uid":216405,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96f014f0dc63b9de8e43168935a12aee33e4411a","tid":1855641,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"tvb訪問啲戴n95但戴得一條繩<br />\n得啖笑"},{"pid":"e977f371fa1affe1c459b130390bb9381f4c8db6","tid":1855641,"uid":228337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢我覺得無齊認證嗰啲都可以用<br />\n你剪開有3層，中間嗰層擋到下水<br />\n望落新淨，有一定嘅厚度<br />\n戴落唔似救救咁一陣臭膠味<br />\n正常外科口罩會有陣「藥水/醫院味」<br />\n唔識點樣形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當然唔係叫你食炒價買無牌嘢咁戇鳩<br />\n而係既然屋企有就頂住檔先"},{"pid":"fa4d15196a6f614b2781c7363b4a2d09830f7402","tid":1855641,"uid":247019,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"香港人做gear 撚就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e562f0ba21d04f032a2f15fb9fbf8f7a681d292","tid":1855641,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"西貢黑警打爆路過呀叔個頭，所有人retweet ！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fight4hongkong/status/1226423205449158656?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffight4hongkong%2Fstatus%2F1226423205449158656%3Fs%3D21&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ima%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=f9bbca04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffight4hongkong%2Fstatus%2F1226423205449158656%3Fs%3D21&h=284cc9c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fight4hongkong/status/1226423205449158656?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手投，尋晚將軍澳果單激嬲Rogers，佢想收集民意take actions<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1226373249837170688?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1226373249837170688%3Fs%3D21&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ima%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=6c1316e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1226373249837170688%3Fs%3D21&h=7ec12114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1226373249837170688?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"be2bb70d9838ae07d69fecccf4d5504676df4de6","tid":1855641,"uid":22362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d98ad1c7d859783171e9bcedad14619a682fc15","tid":1855641,"uid":286131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e089005806c8edda376bc7cabb738d8546fbbc61","tid":1855641,"uid":30510,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif