ick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c26bb3fce8b55535373cd446cbfca397f803781","tid":1855641,"uid":118859,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:38:30.000Z","msg":"其實睇咗咁多post令到我走去問個醫生friend<br />\n<br />\n佢話啲人都癡9線 + 走火入魔。正常人普通口罩夠晒用 (佢自己成家都係就咁用泰國嗰隻klean mask出街)。<br />\n<br />\n佢話要買就買嗰啲酒精搓手液多啲洗手好過"},{"pid":"2923fb7f67e30be8d48323dd5075fc4a8abb3e01","tid":1855641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae8d462fc277cedb1eb870c5fc86b42fee347812","tid":1855641,"uid":112241,"like":101,"dislike":3,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"樓主快的走，我幫你頂住。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:40:26.000Z","msg":"口罩邪教會發爛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fd7f1ddf9300e5947ad4af25f3ad5e3079b428","tid":1855641,"uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70b7ee678c73b3a7a67fbc44eb71889d7be21259","tid":1855641,"uid":14919,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"終於有人出post講防到飛沫就夠 好感動<br />\n之前話唔洗VFE仲俾人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:43:10.000Z","msg":"口罩邪教係唔會容許任何人質疑口罩功用"},{"pid":"419975a0ffb449a0aff66218a124d9d7743fe559","tid":1855641,"uid":14361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1eb4eb2108c93a1b078ee475d5d9edbfdb689115","tid":1855641,"uid":268516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:00:18.000Z","msg":"搞咁撚多野戴個超級勁口罩<br />\n然後原來無洗手習慣<br />\n就咁隨手周圍摸完就戴同除口罩<br />\n或者捽眼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:50:31.000Z","msg":"其實好多人都係咁，我之前見有啲人帶住3M 1870去排火鍋店,講真你口罩幾勁都好自己無防疫意識又咪死，留翻啲勁嘢比醫護仲好啦屌"},{"pid":"85a7e7354e55dd7349f3b701820f0e3e61d24044","tid":1855641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c26bb3fce8b55535373cd446cbfca397f803781","tid":1855641,"uid":118859,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:38:30.000Z","msg":"其實睇咗咁多post令到我走去問個醫生friend<br />\n<br />\n佢話啲人都癡9線 + 走火入魔。正常人普通口罩夠晒用 (佢自己成家都係就咁用泰國嗰隻klean mask出街)。<br />\n<br />\n佢話要買就買嗰啲酒精搓手液多啲洗手好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:54:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">PFE</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BFEVFE95</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">99%ASTM</span> <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">level123PM</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2.5 droplet</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">0.6 &mu;m 。。</span>"},{"pid":"4d0362dd7fe7dc2792265a3fe6525d3dd8a82fe1","tid":1855641,"uid":157697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T01:30:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係連登仔 戴個口罩都都要研究生上身<br />\n<br />\n咁多個防疫手段 口罩只係其中一樣<br />\n<br />\n你其他方面係咪都做到完美極致？<br />\n<br />\n你戴口罩前後有無洗手？掉口罩有無用膠袋包好？電話鎖匙銀包有無每日消毒？<br />\n<br />\n無？你個99%99%99%口罩戴黎托呀？"},{"pid":"7bdd5eee084e5746d39f158192d8db4b3d92ac9b","tid":1855641,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n你知唔知終共hack咗來自三十幾個國家、幾十間 global telecoms 至少七年，竊取了大量 data?? </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191215181157/https://siliconangle.com/2019/06/25/data-stolen-global-telcos-suspected-chinese-hacking-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20191215181157%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fsiliconangle.com%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2Fdata-stolen-global-telcos-suspected-chinese-hacking-campaign&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ima%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=a1b2bd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20191215181157/https://siliconangle.com/2019/06/25/data-stolen-global-telcos-suspected-chinese-hacking-campaign</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想睇吓點可以阻到終共 track 你？即刻撳入嚟睇:</span></span></strong><